properties.text:
Thank you for downloading this modpack. I've spent a lot of time putting it together and tried to keep it a cohesive and balanced experience that is fun to play.

There a lot of changes made to the mods you may be used to playing as well 
as some mods you may have never played before. Use this guide to learn about anything in this pack.

If this wiki doesn't have the information you were looking for, or you believe you have found a bug with the modpack, please submit a report to the modpack Github issue tracker.
